CONTRACT classification
  SHAPE: {label: enum(spam|ham), confidence: float}

STEP load_message
  TAKES: path:    str
  GIVES: message: str
  MODE:  exact
  LANG:  python

STEP classify
  TAKES: message:        str
  GIVES: classification: classification
  MODE:  judgment

FLOW spam_filter
  load_message(path="msg.txt")
    -> classify(message)
